title: Bozo's Circus Clip (Jan 1979)
description: First 10 minutes of an episode of Chicago&#039;s Bozo&#039;s Circus that took place during the 79 blizzard. Host Frazier Thomas fails to make it to the studio. Since the show was broadcast live in those days the rest of the crew had to cope with the absence. In the show Cooky (the second banana) tries to &#039;take over&#039; the show in Frazier&#039;s absence and hilarity ensues.
